n0:createSxmlObject.n0:source: <VIEW xmlns="http://xmlns.oracle.com/ku" version="1.0"> <SCHEMA>SIMDEV</SCHEMA> <NAME>VF1_LAPFRAMES</NAME> <DEFAULT_COLLATION>USING_NLS_COMP</DEFAULT_COLLATION> <COL_LIST> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>M_SESSION</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>LAP</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>STARTF</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>ENDF</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> </COL_LIST> <SUBQUERY>select DISTINCT l."DATA$m_session" m_session, l."DATA$m_current_lap_num" lap, MIN(l."DATA$m_frame") OVER (PARTITION BY l."DATA$m_session", l."DATA$m_current_lap_num" ORDER BY l."DATA$m_session", l."DATA$m_current_lap_num") startf, MAX(l."DATA$m_frame") OVER (PARTITION BY l."DATA$m_session", l."DATA$m_current_lap_num" ORDER BY l."DATA$m_session", l."DATA$m_current_lap_num") endf FROM "F1SIM-LAPDATA" l</SUBQUERY> </VIEW>
